{"tid":1637513,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"澄清：Apple 唔肯印「光復香港 時代革命」比我","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T08:16:56.000Z","uid":153833,"like":776,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8b5b11d57a0efa80779669e89c61e3e91274ac","tid":1637513,"uid":153833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1637362/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1637362/page/1</a><br />\n話說上個post係買左部airpods但收唔到gift message，又揾過客服問，又send過email去apple問但一個回覆都無，搞到我同個frd一肚氣<br />\n<br />\n但經過巴絲係入面俾既資料，原來gift message只係印係張invoice到就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVBTD7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVBTD7g.png&h=857133c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞到我地滿心期待呢個樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scnrY4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscnrY4T.png&h=8d89098c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以long in short: 7左＋炒車<br />\n今次做法係不完美，下次會改善返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該曬各位巴絲幫我搞清楚件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位繼續支持apple~"},{"pid":"798286d7663e0a7c85f136a0391a3054edb3e937","tid":1637513,"uid":25108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27a93df5a749ed48d17baa88d1d01d7e8c22088","tid":1637513,"uid":308567,"like":228,"dislike":5,"score":223,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"戅鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319560dfa82a7ad434b0a6412c8f8bc4a7a90cd1","tid":1637513,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f19e235d52