b575976612d5b6","tid":1637513,"uid":270943,"like":114,"dislike":9,"score":105,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"話說早排訂左個airpods做禮物比朋友，特別加左個雷射＋gift message<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APRPWEq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPRPWEq.png&h=fad6cef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到係上海寄出黎都心知不妙，驚關都過唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3X7Jjx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3X7Jjx.png&h=4fe0f44f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後終於收到，結果係完全無印到「光復香港 時代革命」比我！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXOZzrj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXOZzrj.jpg&h=9be340e6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n揾左客服追問，佢叫我揾售後，send左電郵去售後投訴，過左成個星期都無回覆過我<br />\n馬上負評佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vf8F3jZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVf8F3jZ.png&h=fb4b7737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7B0QF6y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7B0QF6y.png&h=eb6006b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然我知大家都係用apple產品，要大家棄用iphone甚至裝修apple都係無可能既事連我都唔建議大家去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但想比大家知道，繼上次唔俾HKmap.live上架（最尾終於上左）<br />\n今次連印句口號都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來就算係Apple ,都係有政治審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到依家都無收到任何apple既回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同朋友依家係對apple十分之失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後， 光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcc7b5eea15f53511b775965a208415a56d5061","tid":1637513,"uid":158524,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝笑料"},{"pid":"4461b56d5266869dba210702cd23bfaf0a407e0a","tid":1637513,"uid":20084,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:14:40.000Z","msg":"炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab16cf7f40ddff1e5041353858817c9e588b199","tid":1637513,"uid":266172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:15:51.000Z","msg":"屌。。"},{"pid":"00e3436538c3383cf39c66623af8374bb427410b","tid":1637513,"uid":69737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07c106638630c5d226d57723129cf13cb576b38","tid":1637513,"uid":156509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚死，我諗真係唔係個個知"},{"pid":"5809a8a8faa3e41e240010c0aaa8640268c147a7","tid":1637513,"uid":147367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"柒到彈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26f8dc27396a31f3ba205f4f76616cf089c7662","tid":1637513,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"［圍觀師第一次出動］今晚去黨鐵站 （文宣好機會）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},